# Profit Or Loss Non Current Assets Disposal Groups Held For Sale Not Discontinued Operation Losses Amount

## identifier
de13813

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, for any losses on the measurement of non-current assets (or disposal groups); classified as held for sale that does not meet the definition of discontinued operation. This item must be reported in accordance with the relevant accounting standard.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.NonCurrentAssetsDisposalGroupsHeldForSaleNotDiscontinuedOperationLosses.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.19
- period=duration
